Package: ife
Title: Treatment Effects in Interactive Fixed Effects Models
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Brantly", "Callaway", email = "brantly.callaway@temple.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Estimates the Average Treatment Effect for the Treated (ATT) in interactive fixed effects models.  These are models where the effect of time invariant unobserved heterogeneity can change in unrestricted ways across time.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.4)
